    <div class="message-content">
      <h2>üåº G·ª≠i t·∫∑ng em üåº</h2>
      <p>Nh√¢n ng√†y 20/10, ch√∫c em lu√¥n r·∫°ng r·ª°, t·ª± tin v√† g·∫∑p th·∫≠t nhi·ªÅu ni·ªÅm vui trong cu·ªôc s·ªëng. Mong r·∫±ng nh·ªØng ƒëi·ªÅu t·ªët ƒë·∫πp nh·∫•t s·∫Ω lu√¥n ƒë·∫øn v·ªõi em ‚Äî c√¥ g√°i tuy·ªát v·ªùi m√† ai g·∫∑p c≈©ng ph·∫£i m·ªâm c∆∞·ªùi üòä</p>
      <button class="close-btn" id="closeBtn">ƒê√≥ng l·∫°i</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="confetti" id="confetti"></div>

  <script>
    const envelope = document.getElementById('envelope');
    const messageBox = document.getElementById('messageBox');
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById('closeBtn');
    const confettiRoot = document.getElementById('confetti');

    envelope.addEventListener('click', () => {
      envelope.classList.add('open');
      setTimeout(() => {
        messageBox.style.display = 'flex';
        burstConfetti();
      }, 600);
    });

    closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      messageBox.style.display = 'none';
      envelope.classList.remove('open');
    });

    function rand(min, max) { return Math.random() * (max - min) + min; }
    function createPiece() {
      const el = document.createElement('span');
      el.style.left = rand(0, 100) + '%';
      el.style.top = rand(-10, 10) + '%';
      el.style.background = `hsl(${rand(0,360)},70%,60%)`;
      el.style.transform = `rotate(${rand(0,360)}deg)`;
      el.style.opacity = 1;
      el.style.transition = 'transform 1.6s linear, top 1.6s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1), opacity 1.6s linear';
      confettiRoot.appendChild(el);
      requestAnimationFrame(() => {
        el.style.top = '120%';
        el.style.transform = `translateY(0) rotate(${rand(360,720)}deg)`;
        el.style.opacity = 0;
      });
      setTimeout(() => el.remove(), 1700);
    }
    function burstConfetti() {
      for (let i = 0; i < 50; i++) setTimeout(createPiece, i * 10);
    }
  </script>
